M|ai-prompt-architecture|name: ai-prompt-architecture
M|ai-prompt-architecture|description: >-
M|ai-prompt-architecture|AI Image Prompt Architecture for Pixel. Model-specific parameter optimization, consistency across batches, seed management, rejection pattern analysis.
M|ai-prompt-architecture|version: 1.0.0
M|ai-prompt-architecture|platforms: []
M|ai-prompt-architecture|metadata:
M|ai-prompt-architecture|hermes:
M|ai-prompt-architecture|tags: [dev, nextjs, typescript, architecture, vercel, api-routes, build, yvon]
M|ai-prompt-architecture|tec framework for generating consistent, high-quality image batches across AI models.
M|ai-prompt-architecture|Build every prompt from these components in order:
M|ai-prompt-architecture|[Subject], [Setting], [Lighting]. [Style descriptor], [Composition]. [Mood adjectives]
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Subject: Who/what is the focus. "A woman in a cream linen blazer"
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Setting: Environment, background. "standing against a textured plaster wall"
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Lighting: Light quality and direction. "soft north-facing morning light"
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Style: Genre, visual tradition. "editorial fashion photography"
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Composition: Framing, camera angle. "medium shot, rule of thirds"
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Mood: Emotional tone. "effortless, quiet confidence"
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- `--ar` for aspect ratio (1:1, 16:9, 9:16)
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- `--style raw` for less AI interpretation
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- `--s 100-250` for less stylization (tighter to prompt)
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- `--v 6` for latest model version
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Include style keywords directly in the prompt
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Specify "photorealistic" for photo-like output
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Use "no text, no watermark" in negative guidance
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Use clear subject descriptions
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Add camera/lens terms for photographic quality
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Specify lighting conditions for mood control
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Same seed produces similar composition
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Different seed, same prompt: tests model variation range
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Lock seed for variations of a single concept (change one component, keep seed)
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- doc every seed: record seed, output quality, usable yes/no
M|ai-prompt-architecture|**Seed Log Format:**
M|ai-prompt-architecture|```
M|ai-prompt-architecture|Batch: {id} | Model: {name} | Prompts: {n}
M|ai-prompt-architecture|Seed -> Quality -> Verdict
M|ai-prompt-architecture|1234567 -> Sharp, natural -> PASS
M|ai-prompt-architecture|2345678 -> Slight artifact on hand -> FAIL
M|ai-prompt-architecture|3456789 -> Background too busy -> FAIL
M|ai-prompt-architecture|```
M|ai-prompt-architecture|1. **Style anchor**: Include the same style phrase in every prompt ("editorial minimalism, natural lighting, clean backgrounds")
M|ai-prompt-architecture|2. **Color lock**: Specify exact colors ("warm cream tones, sage green accent, charcoal shadows")
M|ai-prompt-architecture|3. **Reference image**: When possible, use image prompting with a brand-coherent reference
M|ai-prompt-architecture|4. **Avoid list**: Lock the avoid list across all prompts for a vtr
M|ai-prompt-architecture|Track which prompt elements correlate with low-quality outputs:
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- If specific hand poses fail repeatedly (>30% rejection rate), avoid hands in prompts; crop or reframe
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- If complex backgrounds fail (>25%), simplify background description
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- If multiple subjects fail (>40%), gen single subject, composite later
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- If specific text in image fails (>60%), add text in post-prd, not generation
M|ai-prompt-architecture|Update the Style Spec based on rejection data. If a pattern exceeds 25% rejection rate, it should be added to the Avoid list.
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Style terms: editorial, fashion photography, natural light, textured
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Colors: warm neutrals, muted tones, brand palette accents
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Mood: confident, effortless, editorial
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Lighting: soft, natural, directional
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Style terms: clean, modern, tech-forward, professional
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Colors: white space, brand palette, light backgrounds
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Mood: trustworthy, confident, approachable
M|ai-prompt-architecture|- Lighting: bright, clean, evenly lit